{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/opengl-screen-space-object-manipulation/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"54b877f2-4317-5a3c-b72b-accd9ebfa000","html":"<p>ⓒ 2019. <a href=\"https://media.korea.ac.kr/people/jhan/\">JungHyun Han</a> Korea University Seoul, All rights reserved.</p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"object-picking\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#object-picking\" aria-label=\"object picking permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Object Picking</h2>\n<p>어떠한 픽셀을 클릭했을 때, 해당 픽셀이 포함된 물체가 선택되는 현상을 구현해보자.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"objectpicking\"\n        title=\"objectpicking\"\n        src=\"/static/5a4484f610c644e36b323d3769676ffc/37523/objectpicking.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5a4484f610c644e36b323d3769676ffc/e9ff0/objectpicking.png 180w,\n/static/5a4484f610c644e36b323d3769676ffc/f21e7/objectpicking.png 360w,\n/static/5a4484f610c644e36b323d3769676ffc/37523/objectpicking.png 720w,\n/static/5a4484f610c644e36b323d3769676ffc/302a4/objectpicking.png 1080w,\n/static/5a4484f610c644e36b323d3769676ffc/8cdda/objectpicking.png 1168w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ray : 어떤 시작점에서 한쪽 방향으로의 직선. 여기에는 start point랑 Direction vector가 있다고 생각해보자.</li>\n<li>이 Ray가 쭉 버떠나갔을 때 어디와 마주치는지를 확인해보자.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Object space → World space → Camera space → Clips space → Screen space 이 전체의 스페이스 변환을 보아도 object간 구별을 확인한 적이 없다.</p>\n<p>ray-object intersection Test에서 Object가 첫번째로 ray에 닿는 순간을 찾으면 될꺼 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>하지만 이는 screen-space에서는 해당 정보가 없기 때문에, Object Space공간에서 해결해야 할 것이다.</li>\n<li>screen space에서 클릭이 실행되기 때문에, 해당 과정을 거꾸로 거슬러 올라가야한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"camera-space-ray\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#camera-space-ray\" aria-label=\"camera space ray permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Camera-space Ray</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cameraSpace\"\n        title=\"cameraSpace\"\n        src=\"/static/5d68a1d33ba60477d421c0a33d56b1f0/37523/cameraSpace.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d68a1d33ba60477d421c0a33d56b1f0/e9ff0/cameraSpace.png 180w,\n/static/5d68a1d33ba60477d421c0a33d56b1f0/f21e7/cameraSpace.png 360w,\n/static/5d68a1d33ba60477d421c0a33d56b1f0/37523/cameraSpace.png 720w,\n/static/5d68a1d33ba60477d421c0a33d56b1f0/302a4/cameraSpace.png 1080w,\n/static/5d68a1d33ba60477d421c0a33d56b1f0/f8836/cameraSpace.png 1214w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ray는 카메라 공간으로 변환을 해야한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>camera-space ray의 시작점의 z좌표는 -n임을 이용해서 (xs, xc, yc)를 구해볼 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>projection transform을 사용해 4x4 행렬 camera-space 시작점에 적용을 하면 clip공간의 시작점을 얻을 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>거기에 viewport transform을 적용하면, 스크린 공간의 시작점을 알 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.22222222222223%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"calculation\"\n        title=\"calculation\"\n        src=\"/static/9dac051e3a5f090dc33c8d4421fe103d/37523/calculation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9dac051e3a5f090dc33c8d4421fe103d/e9ff0/calculation.png 180w,\n/static/9dac051e3a5f090dc33c8d4421fe103d/f21e7/calculation.png 360w,\n/static/9dac051e3a5f090dc33c8d4421fe103d/37523/calculation.png 720w,\n/static/9dac051e3a5f090dc33c8d4421fe103d/b4098/calculation.png 816w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<em>xc와 yc는 따로 계산되어서 산출할 수 있다.</em></p>\n<p>추가로, 카메라 공간에서의 projection line은 모두 원점으로 수렴했었던 걸 배웠다. 시작점을 알고 있다면, 원점과 시작점을 잇는다면 그것을 방향벡터로 설정할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vectorCal\"\n        title=\"vectorCal\"\n        src=\"/static/d6da0d444632b996d371eca9dadeb958/37523/vectorCal.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d6da0d444632b996d371eca9dadeb958/e9ff0/vectorCal.png 180w,\n/static/d6da0d444632b996d371eca9dadeb958/f21e7/vectorCal.png 360w,\n/static/d6da0d444632b996d371eca9dadeb958/37523/vectorCal.png 720w,\n/static/d6da0d444632b996d371eca9dadeb958/a1792/vectorCal.png 780w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<em>w coordinate가 0이라면 벡터를 의미한다.</em></p>\n<br/>\n<h3 id=\"object-space-ray\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#object-space-ray\" aria-label=\"object space ray permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Object-space Ray</h3>\n<br/>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#object-picking\">Object Picking</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#camera-space-ray\">Camera-space Ray</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#object-space-ray\">Object-space Ray</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"ⓒ 2019. JungHyun Han Korea University Seoul, All rights reserved. Object Picking 어떠한 픽셀을 클릭했을 때, 해당 픽셀이 포함된 물체가 선택되는 현상을 구현해보자.  Ray : 어떤 시작점에서 한쪽 방향으로의 직선. 여기에는 start point랑 Direction vector가 있다고 생각해보자. 이 Ray가 쭉 버떠나갔을 때 어디와 마주치는지를 확인해보자. Object space → World space → Camera space → Clips space → Screen space 이 전체의 스페이스 변환을 보아도 object간 구별을 확인한 적이 없다. ray-object intersection Test에서 Object가 첫번째로 ray에 닿는 순간을 찾으면 될꺼 같다. 하지만 이는 screen-space에서는 해당 정보가 없기 때문에, Object Space공간에서 해결해야 할 것이다. screen space에…","frontmatter":{"date":"October 13, 2024","title":"OpenGL ES 3차원 컴퓨터그래픽스 Screen-space Object Manipulation","categories":"OpenGL","author":"ALEX","emoji":"🥽"},"fields":{"slug":"/opengl-screen-space-object-manipulation/"}},"next":{"id":"d93d5561-d9d9-59e9-9537-b28db33561a0","html":"<p>ⓒ 2019. <a href=\"https://media.korea.ac.kr/people/jhan/\">JungHyun Han</a> Korea University Seoul, All rights reserved.</p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"euler-transforms\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#euler-transforms\" aria-label=\"euler transforms permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Euler Transforms</h2>\n<p>물체를 여러 축(Principal Axes)을 기준으로 연속적으로 회전시킬 때, 물체는 새로운 임의의 방향을 갖게 된다. 이 방법을 통해 물체의 방향을 결정하는 것이 “Euler Transform”이라고 부르기로 함.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"eulerTransform\"\n        title=\"eulerTransform\"\n        src=\"/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/37523/eulerTransform.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/e9ff0/eulerTransform.png 180w,\n/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/f21e7/eulerTransform.png 360w,\n/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/37523/eulerTransform.png 720w,\n/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/302a4/eulerTransform.png 1080w,\n/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/07a9c/eulerTransform.png 1440w,\n/static/923fc543db15763d122124d1af435029/aa440/eulerTransform.png 1500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Euler Angle은 여기서 Euler Angles(오일러 각): 회전할 때 사용하는 각도들로, 여기서는 𝜃1, θ2, θ3로 나타낸다. 이 각도들은 각각 다른 축을 기준으로 하는 회전을 가지게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>이때 x,y,z에서 어느 축을 먼저 건드리느냐에 따라 결과물이 달라지게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.111111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"orderEulerTransform\"\n        title=\"orderEulerTransform\"\n        src=\"/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/37523/orderEulerTransform.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/e9ff0/orderEulerTransform.png 180w,\n/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/f21e7/orderEulerTransform.png 360w,\n/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/37523/orderEulerTransform.png 720w,\n/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/302a4/orderEulerTransform.png 1080w,\n/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/07a9c/orderEulerTransform.png 1440w,\n/static/28bee91fa9d3a857399b515ce8c9246a/891d5/orderEulerTransform.png 1520w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<em>축의 순서에 따라 결과가 달라지는걸 볼 수 있다.</em></p>\n<h3 id=\"key-frame-animation-in-2d\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#key-frame-animation-in-2d\" aria-label=\"key frame animation in 2d permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Key Frame Animation in 2D</h3>\n<p>고전에는 keyframe에는 메인 keyframe이 있고, 그 메인 keyframe들 사이를 채우는 in-between frames가 있다고 한다.</p>\n<p>하지만 요즘에는 real-time computer animation이 이 사이를 다 automatically 채워주기 시작함.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>여기서 또 중요한 개념이 interpolation이 되겠다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.555555555555554%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"interpolation\"\n        title=\"interpolation\"\n        src=\"/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/37523/interpolation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/e9ff0/interpolation.png 180w,\n/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/f21e7/interpolation.png 360w,\n/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/37523/interpolation.png 720w,\n/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/302a4/interpolation.png 1080w,\n/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/07a9c/interpolation.png 1440w,\n/static/9d94912e57e082bd6c9030253b33fe25/161ec/interpolation.png 1840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"interpolation의-예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#interpolation%EC%9D%98-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"interpolation의 예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Interpolation의 예시</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.22222222222223%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"keyframe\"\n        title=\"keyframe\"\n        src=\"/static/c418942d0a73899b955deef8a9d434d4/37523/keyframe.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c418942d0a73899b955deef8a9d434d4/e9ff0/keyframe.png 180w,\n/static/c418942d0a73899b955deef8a9d434d4/f21e7/keyframe.png 360w,\n/static/c418942d0a73899b955deef8a9d434d4/37523/keyframe.png 720w,\n/static/c418942d0a73899b955deef8a9d434d4/302a4/keyframe.png 1080w,\n/static/c418942d0a73899b955deef8a9d434d4/53639/keyframe.png 1358w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>위 그림에서 keyframe 0, keyframe 1, keyframe 2 이렇게 3개의 메인 keyframe안에서 in-between keyframe들이 interpolation을 통해 생성되는 것을 볼 수 있을 것이다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>꼭 rotation과 Position 뿐만 아니라, 색깔까지도 interpolation이 가능하다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"problemInterpolation\"\n        title=\"problemInterpolation\"\n        src=\"/static/7d356868a5757aeed927ff92f66e01b6/37523/problemInterpolation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7d356868a5757aeed927ff92f66e01b6/e9ff0/problemInterpolation.png 180w,\n/static/7d356868a5757aeed927ff92f66e01b6/f21e7/problemInterpolation.png 360w,\n/static/7d356868a5757aeed927ff92f66e01b6/37523/problemInterpolation.png 720w,\n/static/7d356868a5757aeed927ff92f66e01b6/d48f1/problemInterpolation.png 796w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>만약 keyframe0의 위치가 yz평면 위에 위치해 있고, keyframe1의 위치 또한 yz평면 위에 위치해 있다면, 이 중간에 있는 in-between keyframe들은 당연히 yz평면 위에 놓여 있다고 생각이 들 것이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>근데, interpolation으로 중간 frame을 보면, x좌표값이 0.3으로 되어 있는 것을 볼 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"quaternion\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#quaternion\" aria-label=\"quaternion permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quaternion</h2>\n<p>쿼터니언은 4개의 성분(x, y, z, w)으로 이루어져 있다. 해당 성분은 벡터(x, y, z)와 스칼라(w)를 의미하게 되고, 아래와 같은 성질들이 나타난다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"quaternion\"\n        title=\"quaternion\"\n        src=\"/static/89ca93d6dd7e4f391f7f1b86e4127048/37523/quaternion.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/89ca93d6dd7e4f391f7f1b86e4127048/e9ff0/quaternion.png 180w,\n/static/89ca93d6dd7e4f391f7f1b86e4127048/f21e7/quaternion.png 360w,\n/static/89ca93d6dd7e4f391f7f1b86e4127048/37523/quaternion.png 720w,\n/static/89ca93d6dd7e4f391f7f1b86e4127048/136a2/quaternion.png 884w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>해당 성질을 이용해서 역행렬 성질도 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p><em><em>(pq)-1 = q-1</em> p-1</em>*</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Magnitude : If the magnitude of a quaternion is 1, it’s called a unit quaternion.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<h3 id=\"2d-rotation-through-complex-numbers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2d-rotation-through-complex-numbers\" aria-label=\"2d rotation through complex numbers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2D Rotation through Complex Numbers</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2dQuaternion\"\n        title=\"2dQuaternion\"\n        src=\"/static/5510e391849301b623120ae63f03716a/37523/2dQuaternion.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5510e391849301b623120ae63f03716a/e9ff0/2dQuaternion.png 180w,\n/static/5510e391849301b623120ae63f03716a/f21e7/2dQuaternion.png 360w,\n/static/5510e391849301b623120ae63f03716a/37523/2dQuaternion.png 720w,\n/static/5510e391849301b623120ae63f03716a/eb3fa/2dQuaternion.png 1026w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>(x,y)를 x+yi로 나타내고 이를 complex number <code class=\"language-text\">p</code>라고 하자.</li>\n<li>회전각도 θ를 바탕으로 unit-length complex number을 생각할 수 있는데, 이를 cosθ + sinθi 라고 가정하자.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAa0lEQVQI1z2NWwrDMBADc/9bpknseBc/oKltcNkpmKQCgaSP0WJmTJnhnCOIkmJCgrBt+9zW9YVqnH0/HLU1xhjTtVbG+N4IY3nCA+69k3PG+5MYE6UUjsMhqryvCxHFn4GYEuE+/dT2B/4AcbSZKfKHPNQAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pq\"\n        title=\"pq\"\n        src=\"/static/1f5c74816259ca04f48b368b292f1966/37523/pq.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1f5c74816259ca04f48b368b292f1966/e9ff0/pq.png 180w,\n/static/1f5c74816259ca04f48b368b292f1966/f21e7/pq.png 360w,\n/static/1f5c74816259ca04f48b368b292f1966/37523/pq.png 720w,\n/static/1f5c74816259ca04f48b368b292f1966/ecf19/pq.png 948w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>놀랍게도, 실수부와 허수부가 rotation을 의미하겠금 계산된 것을 볼 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3d-rotation-through-quaternions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3d-rotation-through-quaternions\" aria-label=\"3d rotation through quaternions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3D Rotation through Quaternions</h3>\n<p>3D에서는 축이 필요한데, 이 축을 기준으로 θ만큼 회전한다고 가정해보자.</p>\n<br/>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.111111111111114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3dQuaternion\"\n        title=\"3dQuaternion\"\n        src=\"/static/b2ee6171a288eb656434567ea9dc4151/37523/3dQuaternion.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b2ee6171a288eb656434567ea9dc4151/e9ff0/3dQuaternion.png 180w,\n/static/b2ee6171a288eb656434567ea9dc4151/f21e7/3dQuaternion.png 360w,\n/static/b2ee6171a288eb656434567ea9dc4151/37523/3dQuaternion.png 720w,\n/static/b2ee6171a288eb656434567ea9dc4151/302a4/3dQuaternion.png 1080w,\n/static/b2ee6171a288eb656434567ea9dc4151/75a80/3dQuaternion.png 1134w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>이는 꼭 x,y,z축에서만 회전이 가능하게 하는 것이 아닌, 임의의 u축의 회전도 지원하게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>일반적으로 벡터는 3차원 공간에서 (𝑝𝑥,𝑝𝑦,𝑝𝑧)와 같은 3D 좌표로 나타낼 수 있는데, 쿼터니언으로 변환할 때에는 𝑝 = (𝑝,0) 와 같이 4D로 확장하게 된다. 𝑝𝑣는 벡터 부분(3차원 벡터), 𝑝𝑤 = 0 는 스칼라 부분을 의미한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>회전을 표현하는 공식인 𝑞𝑝𝑞∗ 를 계산합니다. 여기서 𝑞∗는 쿼터니언 𝑞의 켤레를 의미한다. 계산의 결과에서 벡터 부분은 회전된 벡터를 나타냅니다. 즉, **이 결과의 허수 부분(벡터 부분)**이 우리가 원하는 회전된 벡터 𝑝′를 나타내게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"quaternion-interpolation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#quaternion-interpolation\" aria-label=\"quaternion interpolation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quaternion Interpolation</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.22222222222223%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"InterpolationQuaternions\"\n        title=\"InterpolationQuaternions\"\n        src=\"/static/db5dcec74efa6bff67cabc101cf2a910/37523/InterpolationQuaternions.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/db5dcec74efa6bff67cabc101cf2a910/e9ff0/InterpolationQuaternions.png 180w,\n/static/db5dcec74efa6bff67cabc101cf2a910/f21e7/InterpolationQuaternions.png 360w,\n/static/db5dcec74efa6bff67cabc101cf2a910/37523/InterpolationQuaternions.png 720w,\n/static/db5dcec74efa6bff67cabc101cf2a910/302a4/InterpolationQuaternions.png 1080w,\n/static/db5dcec74efa6bff67cabc101cf2a910/e9d87/InterpolationQuaternions.png 1176w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>임의의 t값으로 우리는 interpolation을 진행할 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>p와 q의 내적 값은 각각이 unit 벡터이기 때문에 그냥 cosθ 임을 알 수 있다. 그렇다면, 두 quarternion의 계산을 arcos계산을 통해 θ값을 역으로 구할 수 있게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>구 표면을 이용한 spherical linear interpolation, 이른바 <strong>slerp</strong>이라고 부른다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>4x4행렬로 여태까지 transformation, scaling을 포함한 affine 변환을 다뤄왔다. 만약 quarternion을 이용하게 된다면, 나머지 transformation과 scaling등과는 어떻게 연계를 할 수 있을까?</p>\n<h3 id=\"quaternion-to-matrix\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#quaternion-to-matrix\" aria-label=\"quaternion to matrix permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quaternion to Matrix</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"matrix\"\n        title=\"matrix\"\n        src=\"/static/1c7e0437cafdb848ad3226e35e57fe8a/37523/matrix.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1c7e0437cafdb848ad3226e35e57fe8a/e9ff0/matrix.png 180w,\n/static/1c7e0437cafdb848ad3226e35e57fe8a/f21e7/matrix.png 360w,\n/static/1c7e0437cafdb848ad3226e35e57fe8a/37523/matrix.png 720w,\n/static/1c7e0437cafdb848ad3226e35e57fe8a/38af3/matrix.png 894w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>A quaternion q representing a rotation can be converted into a matrix form. If q = (qx,qy,qz,qw), the rotation matrix is defined as follows.</p>\n<br/>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#euler-transforms\">Euler Transforms</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#key-frame-animation-in-2d\">Key Frame Animation in 2D</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#interpolation%EC%9D%98-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">Interpolation의 예시</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#quaternion\">Quaternion</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#2d-rotation-through-complex-numbers\">2D Rotation through Complex Numbers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3d-rotation-through-quaternions\">3D Rotation through Quaternions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#quaternion-interpolation\">Quaternion Interpolation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#quaternion-to-matrix\">Quaternion to Matrix</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 12, 2024","title":"OpenGL ES 3차원 컴퓨터그래픽스 Euler Transforms & Quaternion","categories":"OpenGL","author":"ALEX","emoji":"🥽"},"fields":{"slug":"/opengl-eulertransforms-quaternions/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://dong-chan.com","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"dongckim/dongckim.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/opengl-screen-space-object-manipulation/","nextSlug":"/opengl-eulertransforms-quaternions/","prevSlug":""}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}